Clone repository to your local machine
Copy user-registration folder from source folder into C:\xampp\htdocs\ folder
Open XAMPP and start apache and MySQL server
In phpMyAdmin, create database called "user_registration" and table called "users" with 5 columns:
id - integer, length 11, primary key, auto icrement
name - varchar, length 255
email - varchar, length 255, unique
password - varchar, length 255
Open browser and navigate to: localhost/hopala/registration.php
